groovyx.net.http

Class HttpBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • groovyx.net.http.HttpBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ApacheHttpBuilder, JavaHttpBuilder

    public abstract class HttpBuilder
extends Object
implements Closeable
    The HttpBuilder class is the main entry point into the "Http Builder NG" API. It provides access to the HTTP Client configuration and the HTTP verbs to be executed.
